{"type": "article", "id": 30174, "title": "护发产品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-26T23:02:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160726230333QhPZWOVnEuYm0bsc.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>如果你不曾被专业护发产品的包装惊艳到，设计公司 <a href=\"http://formnation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FormNation</a> 这次为来自美国伊利诺斯州的 Uberliss 全新打造的包装设计或许会让你忍不住驻足端详。黑白两种底色分别代表了针对发廊以及普通用户的两种产品线，上面印有专门设计的手绘图案。这些看上去非常随性的涂鸦其实代表着产品不同的功效，带给人一种耳目一新的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232130Ev0ASndPqGtTlD3O.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.508000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232130vlVg6KNeQEGyY7mH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607262321302dCvlVpfram0q9ZL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.557000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160726232131igjom3xeVMPrY9W6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}